## Provenance

This package consolidates three previously-separate sources:

1. TRUGS-DEVELOPMENT/TRUGS_TOOLS_development/ — private mono-repo folder (folder lifecycle CLIs, branch schemas, web pipeline)
2. TRUGS-LLC/TRUGS/tools/ — memory + TRL + compliance_check + tget/tupdate/tdelete/tunlink (migrated in `trugs` 2.0.0 breaking release)
3. Xepayac/TRUGS-AAA (archived) — aaa_validator.py + canonical AAA reference TRUG

See TRUGS-LLC/TRUGS-DEVELOPMENT#1576 for the reorganization that created this package.
